When to Use What?

This is worth memorizing.

Situation	                        Use
Count connected components once	    DFS/BFS or DSU
Dynamic edge additions	            ✅ DSU
RepeatedAre A and B connected?"	    ✅ DSU
Need actual traversal/path	        DFS/BFS
Shortest path	                    BFS/Dijkstra
Cycles in dependencies	            DFS/Topological Sort 

Example

Suppose there are: 100,000 nodes and 100,000 operations

Operations:- 
union(1,2)

union(5,7)

connected(2,7)

union(2,5)

connected(1,7)

union(9,10)

...

Imagine doing DFS for every connected() query.

😱 That would be terrible.

DSU:

connected(a,b) {

    return find(a) == find(b);
}

done...